## .NET Optimized Gitignore (By Gemini)

# --- Build results ---
[Dd]ebug/
[Dd]ebugPublic/
[Rr]elease/
[Rr]eleases/
x64/
x86/
[Ww][Ii][Nn]32/
[Aa][Rr][Mm]/
[Aa][Rr][Mm]64/
bld/
[Bb]in/
[Oo]bj/
[Ll]og/
[Ll]ogs/

# --- Visual Studio (CHẶN TOÀN BỘ RÁC) ---
# Thay vì liệt kê từng file, dòng này chặn tất cả mọi thứ trong .vs
.vs/
*.suo
*.user
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

# --- .NET Core ---
project.lock.json
project.fragment.lock.json
artifacts/

# --- ASP.NET Scaffolding ---
ScaffoldingReadMe.txt

# --- NuGet Packages ---
*.nupkg
*.snupkg

# --- Others & IDEs ---
.vscode/
.idea/
~$*
*~
CodeCoverage/
*.binlog

# --- Testing (NUnit/MSTest) ---
[Tt]est[Rr]esult*/
[Bb]uild[Ll]og.*
*.VisualState.xml
TestResult.xml
nunit-*.xml
/.claude/settings.local.json
/.claude/launch.json
/MV.PresentationLayer/appsettings.json
/MV.PresentationLayer/appsettings.json
/MV.PresentationLayer/serviceAccountKey.json
/MV.PresentationLayer/appsettings.json
